sentences: Marcela Pavia (born 1957) is an Italian-American composer.
Execution for Percussion Instruments and Drums of the Percussive Arts Society 2007, Italy
Dos para epigrafes El General Lavalle piano four hands, 2004

After receiving her degree, Pavia worked as a composer and taught music at the Universidad Nacional de Rosario, Manuel de Falla Conservatory in Buenos Aires, Universidad del Museo Social Argentino and the Universidad del Salvador in Buenos Aires.
